item.title: CVE-2024-39914|2024-07-12T14:46:44.696Z -- fogproject -- fogproject
item.description: FOG is a cloning/imaging/rescue suite/inventory management system. Prior to 1.5.10.34, packages/web/lib/fog/reportmaker.class.php in FOG was affected by a command injection via the filename parameter to /fog/management/export.php. This vulnerability is fixed in 1.5.10.34.
